src:
Raslistan: Bjässar i farozonen – tio aktier som väntas falla minst 10 procent
I spåren av kvartalsrapporterna har analytikerkåren uppdaterat sin syn på börsbolagens kursutsikter. Di listar de tio bolag som väntas falla med 10–25 procent framöver, varav flera hittas i storbolagsindexet OMXS30.
01 Nov 2019, 08:31 by Christopher Jungstedt

Breed list: Jaws in the danger zone - ten shares expected to fall at least 10 percent
In the wake of the quarterly reports, the analyst corps has updated its view of the stock exchange companies' outlook. They list the ten companies that are expected to fall by 10–25 percent in the future, several of which can be found in the large company index OMXS30.
01 Nov 2019, 08:31 by Christopher Jungstedt
